@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vapwwk(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs(v0))
    tmp = (v2 / (tmp * wp.sin(tmp + 0.27)))
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.97))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs(0.02))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v0 + 0.72) + tmp))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = 0.25
    data[tid] = v0
